<div class="com-share" data-id="11495" data-title="《人类有多擅长虚伪，就有多擅长创造“虚伪”的食物》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/11495/medium/11495.jpg?1436639085" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/11495.html?from=groupmessage&amp;isappinstalled=1" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
